<view class="page">
  <view class="login-stage">
    <view class="hero-card login-hero">
      <view class="login-brand">
        <text class="eyebrow">KITCHEN ACCESS</text>
        <text class="hero-title">3 秒进入点餐</text>
      </view>
      <text class="hero-note">下单、购物车、订单和消息都需要先完成微信授权，一键登录后即可继续操作。</text>
      <view class="hero-ribbon-row">
        <text class="hero-ribbon">地址管理</text>
        <text class="hero-ribbon">订单追踪</text>
        <text class="hero-ribbon">消息提醒</text>
      </view>
      <view class="login-orb login-orb-large"></view>
      <view class="login-orb login-orb-small"></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card login-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">登录后立即可用</text>
      <text class="section-subtitle">为下单流程准备好的 3 项能力</text>
    </view>
    <view class="benefit-grid">
      <view class="benefit-card">
        <text class="benefit-kicker">01</text>
        <text class="benefit-title">一键授权</text>
        <text class="benefit-copy">点击一次就拉起微信授权并完成登录。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="benefit-card">
        <text class="benefit-kicker">02</text>
        <text class="benefit-title">订单同步</text>
        <text class="benefit-copy">下单、配送、完成状态都能快速查看。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="benefit-card benefit-card-wide">
        <text class="benefit-kicker">03</text>
        <text class="benefit-title">自动带资料</text>
        <text class="benefit-copy">登录后自动带上微信昵称和头像，不再手动补资料。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <button class="primary-btn one-tap-btn" bindtap="submitLogin" loading="{{submitting}}">一键微信授权登录</button>
    <text class="login-footnote">继续即表示使用微信昵称和头像完成登录，用于下单与订单同步。</text>
  </view>
</view>
